currentDoc: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

currentSuggestions.original: You ask the other people if they know what's going on.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: You ask the other people if they know what's going on.

currentSuggestions.original: So you all sit there, waiting, wondering what you’ve done in your life to deserve this punishment.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: So you all sit there, waiting, wondering what you’ve done in your life to deserve this punishment.

currentSuggestions.original: The others in the cinema, having worked out that you must have died recently, make polite conversation and ask you about your previous lives.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: The others in the cinema, having worked out that you must have died recently, make polite conversation and ask you about your previous lives.

currentSuggestions.original: Suddenly, you hear a piercing scream in the distance.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Suddenly, you hear a piercing scream in the distance.

currentSuggestions.original: You and your fellow re-incarnations begin to get agitated.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: You and your fellow re-incarnations begin to get agitated.

ops.insert: You ask the other people if they know what's going on.

currentSuggestions.original: Just then, the screen flickers to life, and you see yourself lying in a hospital bed.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Just then, the screen flickers to life, and you see yourself lying in a hospital bed.

currentSuggestions.original: "I'm getting really impatient!" another complains.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I'm getting really impatient!" another complains.

currentSuggestions.trimmed: "This has never happened to me before either," says another.

currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I'm not sure if this is a mistake or what," says another.

currentSuggestions.original: "Maybe it's broken," you say.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "Maybe it's broken," you say.

currentSuggestions.original: "I was just here last week, and I went right from being born to taking my first steps."
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I was just here last week, and I went right from being born to taking my first steps."

currentSuggestions.original: Eventually, the screen flickers and a black-and-white scene comes into view.

currentSuggestions.original: "Why don't we just order popcorn and watch the screen," a third suggests.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "Why don't we just order popcorn and watch the screen," a third suggests.

currentSuggestions.original: "I just hope this doesn't keep us stuck here for good," says another.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "I just hope this doesn't keep us stuck here for good," says another.

currentSuggestions.original: A moment later, a man in front of you turns around.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: A moment later, a man in front of you turns around.

currentSuggestions.original: "It can't be broken," says the first person.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: "It can't be broken," says the first person.

currentSuggestions.original: But the screen suddenly flashes to life, and you see a faint outline of a man eating at a dinner table with his wife and children.

currentSuggestions.original: Just then, the screen flickers.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Just then, the screen flickers.

currentSuggestions.original: But then the screen lights up, and you can all see your new life.
